      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·谷風之什·006.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">無將大車.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>無將大車，祇自塵兮。無思百憂，祇自疷兮。
無將大車，維塵冥冥。無思百憂，不出于熲。
無將大車，維塵雍兮。無思百憂，祇自重兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>1 Do not push forward a waggon; —
You will only raise the dust about yourself.
Do not think of all your anxieties; —
You will only make yourself ill.</seg>
      </tuv>
